RAIT-Melody 2016 Holdings Trust $125,000 Financing | Newest SEC Filings

















Newest Filings











RAIT-Melody 2016 Holdings Trust $125,000 Financing
RAIT-Melody 2016 Holdings Trust just submitted form D announcing $125,000 equity financing.  This is a new filing. RAIT-Melody 2016 Holdings Trust was able to sell $125,000. That is 100% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $125,000. The financing was made by 125 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $1,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-12-29. RAIT-Melody 2016 Holdings Trust is based in  TWO LOGAN SQUARE 100 N. 18TH STREET, 23RD FLOOR PHILADELPHIA 19103. The firm's business is REITS and Finance. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  N/A RAIT-Melody 2016 Holdings, LLC.





